            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Examinons un cas d'utilisation : si <code>isDay</code> est <code>true</code>, nous voulons éteindre les lumières.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isDay = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isDay {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Lights off!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"12\" endIndex=\"16\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Lights off!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>true</code> suivi de <code>isDay</code>.</p></body></html>"
